<p>A rare tornado swept through suburbs north of Paris on Monday, October 20, striking hardest in Ermont and toppling three construction cranes [arabnews.com#1][nytimes.com#1]. Authorities said a construction worker was killed and others were injured as the twister cut across multiple towns [arabnews.com#1][bbc.com#1][euronews.com#1]. The storm damaged buildings and infrastructure, with residents emerging in shock to assess torn roofs and debris-strewn streets [euronews.com#1][france24.com#1]. French media reported it was the country&#x27;s first deadly tornado in 17 years, underscoring how unusual such an event is near the capital [washingtonpost.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/0b31gV9ElH0Ee8g6o4280fdodaXZinWnhSEmM-6H5rALnBZ3POGR1UdHwmXpeYhAAk_WxlwEldtBBd9SeQyMt18WzLRfp0_Gia3zEKXwlJnb5WSPzmvIhTslKxUBImsEva822tQOCohx6KItHFHrh7HamQ1kLT060Q_8vAzdhbJLnCZt35o29w' alt='A collapsed crane which fell during high winds in Ermont, Val-d’Oise, France, on Monday.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Emergency response: Authorities deployed about 80 firefighters, 50 police officers, and 20 SAMU personnel in Ermont to secure sites and assist victims [lemonde.fr#1].</li><li>Damage footprint: Ermont was worst hit, with damage reported across roughly ten nearby districts about 20 km northeast of Paris [arabnews.com#1][euronews.com#1].</li><li>Rare fatality: French reports described this as the country&#x27;s first deadly tornado in 17 years, highlighting the event&#x27;s rarity near Paris [washingtonpost.com#1][nytimes.com#1].</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Val-d&#x27;Oise prefecture: Officials emphasized casualty reports and outlined a substantial emergency deployment to manage crane collapses and storm damage. (<a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/france/video/2025/10/21/rare-tornado-kills-man-in-france-after-toppling-cranes_6746646_7.html'>Le Monde</a>)</li><li>Regional prosecutor: Prosecutor Guirec Le Bras confirmed the death of a construction worker at a building site during the storm. (<a href='https://www.arabnews.com/node/2619684/world'>Arab News (AFP)</a>)</li><li>Weather analysts: Meteorologists highlighted the storm’s unusual lethality in France and examined the dynamics that enabled a brief tornado near Paris. (<a href='https://www.washingtonpost.com/weather/2025/10/21/paris-france-tornado-suburb/'>The Washington Post</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.arabnews.com/node/2619684/world'>Tornado kills one, injures four near French capital</a> - arabnews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.france24.com/en/video/20251021-france-residents-in-shock-after-mini-tornado-hits-north-of-paris'>France: Residents in shock after mini tornado hits north of Paris</a> - france24.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/21/world/europe/tornado-paris-france.html'>Deadly Tornado Hits Suburbs of Paris</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/france/video/2025/10/21/rare-tornado-kills-man-in-france-after-toppling-cranes_6746646_7.html'>Rare tornado kills man in France after toppling cranes</a> - lemonde.fr</li><li><a href='https://www.washingtonpost.com/weather/2025/10/21/paris-france-tornado-suburb/'>What fueled a rare tornado that tore through a Paris suburb</a> - washingtonpost.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/videos/c9864114nemo'>Tornado hits Paris suburbs leaving one dead</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/video/2025/10/21/storm-wreaks-havoc-in-paris-suburbs-leaving-trail-of-destruction'>Storm wreaks havoc in Paris suburbs, leaving trail of destruction</a> - euronews.com</li></ul>